Carbon IMS - Inventory Management System
Version: 2.0.0
Release Date: January 4, 2026
Created By: Mike Cheung

Build Information:
- Python: 3.8+
- Flask: 3.0.0
- Database: SQLite3

Change Log:

v2.0.0 (January 4, 2026)
- Trade Criteria & Generic Allocation system
- Locate Inventory modal with availability checking
- Criteria-specific assignment tracking with snapshot restoration
- Draggable modals across all pages
- FIFO ordering for criteria claims
- Auto-restore criteria on unassign
- Improved reports page

v1.0.0 (December 22, 2025)
- Initial release
- User management with role-based access
- Inventory management with CRUD operations
- Warranty management with serial linking
- Automated backup and restore
- Advanced filtering and sorting
- Pagination support
- Timezone support (EST)
- Password-protected operations
